{"tid":2058132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明報： 有60名署名\"香港市民\"投訴正競逐醫學會會長蔡堅涉違「中傷同業」並CC俾特首辦中聯辦","createTime":"2020-06-10T02:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T04:53:15.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e1d2917f751337bd64beab4a889b9bbb50f65e7","tid":2058132,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:36:01.000Z","msg":"有關投訴電郵以「香港市民」署名，引述蔡堅早前接受《眾新聞》和《蘋果日報》的訪問內容，指稱他詆譭香港醫學會現任主席何仲平和其他會董，違反了醫委會《香港註冊醫生專業守則》裏「中傷同業」和「自我宣傳」條例，要求醫委會「嚴肅處理」。電郵寄至醫委會和醫學會，副本抄送至特首辦、政務司長、保安局長和中聯辦。<br />\n<br />\n詳情 ：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200609/s00001/1591718505105/%e8%94%a1%e5%a0%85%e8%a2%ab%e9%9b%86%e9%ab%94%e6%8a%95%e8%a8%b4%e9%81%95%e5%b0%88%e6%a5%ad%e5%ae%88%e5%89%87-%e7%a8%b1%e7%ab%b6%e9%80%90%e9%86%ab%e5%ad%b8%e6%9c%83%e6%9c%83%e9%95%b7%e6%84%9f%e5%a3%93%e5%8a%9b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200609%2Fs00001%2F1591718505105%2F%25e8%2594%25a1%25e5%25a0%2585%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e9%259b%2586%25e9%25ab%2594%25e6%258a%2595%25e8%25a8%25b4%25e9%2581%2595%25e5%25b0%2588%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e5%25ae%2588%25e5%2589%2587-%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e7%25ab%25b6%25e9%2580%2590%25e9%2586%25ab%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%259c%2583%25e9%2595%25b7%25e6%2584%259f%25e5%25a3%2593%25e5%258a%259b&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVaxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=4dc37dc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200609%2Fs00001%2F1591718505105%2F%25e8%2594%25a1%25e5%25a0%2585%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e9%259b%2586%25e9%25ab%2594%25e6%258a%2595%25e8%25a8%25b4%25e9%2581%2595%25e5%25b0%2588%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e5%25ae%2588%25e5%2589%2587-%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e7%25ab%25b6%25e9%2580%2590%25e9%2586%25ab%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%259c%2583%25e9%2595%25b7%25e6%2584%259f%25e5%25a3%2593%25e5%258a%259b&h=03b85757\" data-auto-link target=\"_bl